rComments: Awesome TA, she really knew her stuff. The class was pretty easy and included a semester long group project that was fairly simple.
Awesome lecturer, really down to earth, easy class and very lenient.

The class is the best way to get the literature and arts requirement out of the way without taking some snooze of class. There is a decent amount of reading, but the topics are modern and relevant. Every week you post online about the reading. The midterm is in class but the final was take home. There's a group video project at the end.
